Question: One image contains two black pencil cases, and the other shows one open black case containing a compartment insert.

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many black pencil cases are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many black pencil cases are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there an open black case containing a compartment insert?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there an open black case containing a compartment insert?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 2 and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
